short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension adds a button to the CivitAI interface that allows you download a given model with Stability Matrix.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension adds a "Download with Stability Matrix" button to civitai.com model pages to download models directly into Stability Matrix. 

The creators of this extension are neither affiliated with nor endorsed by civitai.com.
